cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the problem of Spoken Language Understanding and Slot Filling. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and pre-trained language models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing tasks. It may also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with spoken language, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks.
